    "When learning tasks with emergent language, symbolic languages are acquired for communication through a limited number of tokens.",
    "Therefore, we classify those works under limited bandwidth [60][61][62]64].",
    "• Corrupted Messages.",
    "In this category, messages transmitted among agents can be corrupted due to environmental noise or malicious intentions.",
    "DIAL [72] shows that during training, adding Gaussian noise to the communication channel can push the distribution of messages into two modes to convey different types of information."
  ],
